Module org.postgresql.pljava.internal
Package org.postgresql.pljava.jdbc

Class SQLXMLImpl.StAXResultAdapter

java.lang.Object
org.postgresql.pljava.jdbc.SQLXMLImpl.StAXResultAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
XMLStreamWriter
Enclosing class:
SQLXMLImpl<V extends Datum>
static class SQLXMLImpl.StAXResultAdapter extends Object implements XMLStreamWriter
Class to wrap a StAX XMLStreamWriter and hook the method writeEndDocument to also close the underlying output stream, making the SQLXML object ready to use for storing or returning the value.

      public void writeEndDocument() throws XMLStreamException
